OL,3,CHedgehog Hunt: Bin man mistakenly
OL,4,Ctakes flagship statue from family
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,FDurham County Council has apologised
OL,8,Fto a family business after their
OL,9,Fflagship statue was taken by mistake
OL,10,Fduring the weekly bin collection.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the Hedgehog Bakery in
OL,13,FBishop Aukland took to social media to
OL,14,Fask their customers for help after
OL,15,Fthey realised their wooden hedgehog -
OL,16,Fnamed Horace - had vanished.
