OL,3,CHedgehog Hunt: Bin man mistakenly
OL,4,Ctakes flagship statue from family
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,FThe wooden sculpture was commissioned
OL,8,Fto celebrate the bakery's first
OL,9,Fanniversary of trading in 2023 - and
OL,10,Fstands proudly outside the shop on
OL,11,Fevery open day.
OL,13,FOne follower pointed out that they had
OL,14,Fwitnessed the statue being taken
OL,15,Fduring the bin collection, leading the
OL,16,Ffamily business to check their CCTV -
OL,17,Fwhere they found Horace the hedgehog
OL,18,Fhad been lifted by a bin man.
