OL,3,CHedgehog Hunt: Bin man mistakenly
OL,4,Ctakes flagship statue from family
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,FCCTV footage from the bakery shows the
OL,8,Fbin man mistakingly taking the statue
OL,9,Fas he believed it had been fly-tipped.
OL,10,FCredit: Hedgehog Bakery
OL,12,FDurham County Council have now
OL,13,Freturned the statue, and told ITV Tyne
OL,14,FTees it was a "genuine mistake".
OL,16,FThe Hedgehog Bakery said: "Yesterday
OL,17,Fmy husband had put him (Horace) out as
OL,18,Fnormal, but it wasn't until the
OL,19,Fafternoon that my husband noticed he
OL,20,Fwas missing.
