OL,7,F"We quickly put out a post asking if
OL,8,Fanyone knew anything and just to keep
OL,9,Ftheir eyes open for it. We never
OL,10,Fthought we'd see him again to be
OL,11,Fhonest."
OL,13,FThe bakery said they had heard from
OL,14,FDurham County Council today and they
OL,15,Fexplained the bin man who took Horace
OL,16,F"believed he'd been fly-tipped, which
OL,17,Fis why he ended up in the front of the
OL,18,Fbin truck," they said.
