OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,F"Horace has suffered some damage
OL,8,Fduring his kidnapping but thankfully
OL,9,Fthe worker had him mended before
OL,10,Ffinding out he was our lost Hog."
OL,12,FDurham County Council said in a
OL,13,Fstatement: "We can only apologise to
OL,14,Fthe Hedgehog Bakery for any distress
OL,15,Fcaused and are pleased to confirm the
OL,16,Fstatue has been returned to the
OL,17,Fbusiness this afternoon.
