OL,3,CHedgehog Hunt: Bin man mistakenly
OL,4,Ctakes flagship statue from family
OL,5,Cbusiness
OL,7,F"A member of our local bin crew made a
OL,8,Fgenuine mistake in mistaking the
OL,9,Fstatue for waste as it was kerbside,
OL,10,Fwhere large items are often left for
OL,11,Fcollection. As soon as we realised the
OL,12,Fmistake we contacted the bakery to
OL,13,Fapologise and arrange for the statue
OL,14,Fto be returned.
OL,16,F"We would like to wish the bakery
OL,17,Fevery success in the future."
